---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const title = "Stay";
---

<Layout title={title}>
  <h1>Where to Stay Near Missoula</h1>
  <p>
    Missoula makes a good home base, but it's not the only good option. Depending on
    what you're here for, a small lodge on the Bitterroot, a cabin near Seeley Lake,
    or a guest ranch out toward Rock Creek might put you closer to the water, the
    trailhead, or the quiet you're actually looking for.
  </p>
  <p>
    We cover lodging across greater western Montana within a couple hours of
    Missoula &mdash; downtown hotels, small-town motels, bed and breakfasts, cabins,
    vacation rentals, and guest ranches. Every listing here is a real, currently
    operating business, checked directly rather than pulled from an outdated
    directory.
  </p>
  <p>
    Full listings and comparisons for each region are coming soon.
  </p>
</Layout>